  - documentation
  - support for angles/dihedrals/etc.
  - tools to write custom topology files (e.g., LAMMPS data, gromacs.top, amber)
    for which we no suitable molfile plugin exists. or to generate parameter
    files or input script fragments (HOOMD, LAMMPS, ...).
